============================

liveurl (this project) is licensed under the MIT License — see LICENSE.

The compiled liveurl/liveurld binaries also include the following
third-party Go modules. This list reflects the actual dependency graph
compiled into cmd/liveurl and cmd/liveurld (via `go list -deps`), not
every module in go.sum (some go.sum entries are only test/tooling
dependencies of those modules and are never compiled into the binaries).

Regenerate after dependency changes with, e.g.:
  go list -deps ./cmd/liveurl ./cmd/liveurld | grep '\.' | grep -v '^github.com/Tehman700/liveurl' | sort -u

